reviews.text: It offer a good selection, the wines are properly stored therefore the taste is evolving properly with time. They offer nice quality cheese and hams to accompany the wine. I like the staff who also is able to advice and describe the labels and bottles. It is a good address for wine lovers.
If you like wine then you'll like this place.
